ass="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Aurochs"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Aurochs</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy8auu?Pathfinder-Roleplaying-Game-Bestiary" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Pathfinder RPG Bestiary pg. 174</i></a><br /><b>Monster Entry</b> <a href="MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Aurochs"><i>Link</i></a><br />This large, horned bull has a dirty black hide and an aggressive temper. Its horns are wide and sharp.
<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Aurochs"><i>Click here for full details on the aurochs</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Axe Beak"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Axe Beak</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy8odu?Pathfinder-Roleplaying-Game-Bestiary-3" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Bestiary 3 pg. 311</i></a><br /><b>Monster Entry</b> <a href="MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Axe Beak"><i>Link</i></a><br />This stout bird stands upon two long, muscular legs, each ending in a large, curved talon. A pair of undersized wings sprouts from amid its broad body feathers, as does a powerful neck ending in an avian head armed with a grisly serrated beak.
