<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Brontotherium"><i>Click here for full details on the brontotherium</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Bull of Zagresh">Bull of Zagresh</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy97lw?Pathfinder-Campaign-Setting-Belkzen-Hold-of-the-Orc-Hordes" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Belkzen, Hold of the Orc Hordes pg. 55</i></a><br /><b>Monster Entry</b> <a href="MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Bull of Zagresh"><i>Link</i></a><br />This immense bovine has horns reminiscent of a stag, with daggerlike points spreading more than fifteen feet across.
