<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Cave Salamander"><i>Click here for full details on the cave salamander</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Centipede, Giant"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Centipede, Giant</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/pathfinderRPG/v5748btpy8k8r" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Ultimate Magic pg. 36</i></a><br /><b>Monster Entry</b> <a href="MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Centipede"><i>Link</i></a><br />This lengthy, segmented horror writhes and twists, pulsing its venomous mandibles in search of prey.
