<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Moa"><i>Click here for full details on the moa</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Mokele-Mbembe">Mokele-Mbembe</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy9oge?Pathfinder-Roleplaying-Game-Bestiary-6-Hardcover
