rly ferocious-looking companion. Its speed allows it to strike at its enemies from cover without them knowing what happened.<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Solifugid, Giant"><i>Click here for full details on the solifugid, giant</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Sorico">Sorico</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy97ax?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-85-Fires-of-Creation
