<br /><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Wolliped"><i>Click here for full details on the wolliped</i></a>.<br /><br /><h2 class="title"><a href="DruidCompanions.aspx?ItemName=Worg"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Worg</a></h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy95b1?Pathfinder-Campaign-Setting-Inner-Sea-Combat" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Inner Sea Combat pg. 14</i></a><br /><b>Monster Entry</b> <a href="MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Worg"><i>Link</i></a><br />This unusually large wolf has an evil, almost intelligent light shining in its deep red eyes.
